WEBVTT

00:00:01.548 --> 00:00:02.968
Four years ago,

00:00:02.992 --> 00:00:05.984
a teenage girl changed my life

00:00:06.008 --> 00:00:08.238
in one conversation.

00:00:08.262 --> 00:00:09.579
She was 13 years old,

00:00:09.603 --> 00:00:11.260
she was a friend's little cousin

00:00:11.284 --> 00:00:12.482
and she casually told me

00:00:12.506 --> 00:00:15.773
that she had met the man
she was going to marry.

00:00:16.577 --> 00:00:19.490
So I said, "OK, tell me about him."

00:00:19.894 --> 00:00:23.021
And she told me that his name
was Harry Styles.

00:00:23.045 --> 00:00:24.664
(Laughter)

00:00:24.688 --> 00:00:26.664
So I laughed a little, like you,

00:00:26.688 --> 00:00:29.283
and then she said,
"I know you don't think I'm serious,

00:00:29.307 --> 00:00:31.221
but I'm actually going to be with him.